    "## 一、项目背景介绍\n",
    "通过检测食物卡路里来帮助人们吃更健康的食物,也可以帮助减肥人士快速识别食物的卡路里来帮助判断吃或者不吃，将模型部署在手机APP上，通过拍照识别便捷实现食物检测的效果。"

    "## 二、数据介绍\n",
    "\n",
    "**数据集来自项目[Food_Calories_detection](https://github.com/Bin-ze/Food_Calories_detection)**\n",
    "\n",
    "**已经处理好的VOC数据集，数据格式与前面[PaddleDetection - 数据准备](https://github.com/PaddlePaddle/PaddleDetection/blob/release/2.3/docs/tutorials/PrepareDataSet.md)要求一致**\n",
    "\n",
    "**数据集文件夹(图片)** 名称：JPEGImages\n",
    "\n",
    "包含10，000张分辨率为2m/pixel，尺寸为512 * 512的JPG图片，每张图片的名称按数字排序形如0.jpg，1.jpg。\n",
    "\n",
    "**VOC数据标注文件夹**名称：Annotations\n",
    "\n",
    "xml文件中包含以下字段：\n",
    "\n",
    "* filename，表示图像名称。\n",
    "\n",
    "* size，表示图像尺寸。包括：图像宽度、图像高度、图像深度。\n",
    "```\n",
    "    <size>\n",
    "        <width>512</width>\n",
    "        <height>512</height>\n",
    "        <depth>3</depth>\n",
    "    </size>\n",
    "```\n",
    "\n",
    "* object字段，表示每个物体。\n",
    "\t\n",
    "\n",
    "| name |  物体类别名称 |\n",
    "| -------- | -------- |\n",
    "| pose     | 关于目标物体姿态描述（非必须字段）     |\n",
    "| difficult| 难以识别的物体标记为difficult（非必须字段）|\n",
    "| bndbox子标签    | (xmin,ymin) 左上角坐标，(xmax,ymax) 右下角坐标，    | \n",
    "```\n",
    "    <object>\n",
    "        <name>xiangjiao</name>\n",
    "        <pose>Unspecified</pose>\n",
    "        <truncated>0</truncated>\n",
    "        <difficult>0</difficult>\n",
    "        <bndbox>\n",
    "            <xmin>171</xmin>\n",
    "            <ymin>195</ymin>\n",
    "            <xmax>326</xmax>\n",
    "            <ymax>322</ymax>\n",
    "        </bndbox>\n",
    "    </object>\n",
    "```\n",
    "**train.txt 是训练数据集文件列表（占数据集90%）；val.txt 是验证集文件（占数据集10%）**"
   ]

    "# 生成 train.txt 和 valid.txt\n",
    "import os\n",
    "%cd\n",
    "path_origin = 'Food_voc/images/'\n",
    "path_jpg = \"images/\"\n",
    "path_xml = 'annotations/'\n",
    "pic_dir = os.listdir(path_origin)\n",
    "\n",
    "f_train = open('Food_voc/train.txt', 'w')\n",
    "f_val = open('Food_voc/valid.txt', 'w')\n",
    "\n",
    "for i in range(len(pic_dir)):\n",
    "    if i % 30 != 0:\n",
    "        f_train.write(path_jpg + pic_dir[i] + ' ' + path_xml + pic_dir[i].split('.')[0] + '.xml' + '\\n')\n",
    "    else:\n",
    "        f_val.write(path_jpg + pic_dir[i] + ' ' + path_xml + pic_dir[i].split('.')[0] + '.xml' + '\\n')\n",
    "\n",
    "f_train.close()\n",
    "f_val.close()"

    "**优化器配置文件 optimizer_270e.yml**\n",
    "```\n",
    "epoch: 10 #总训练轮数\n",
    "\n",
    "LearningRate:\n",
    "  base_lr: 0.00025 #单卡训练除以8\n",
    "  \n",
    "  # 学习率调整策略\n",
    "  schedulers:\n",
    "  - !PiecewiseDecay\n",
    "    gamma: 0.1\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # 学习率变化位置(轮数)\n",
    "    milestones:\n",
    "    - 4\n",
    "    - 7\n",
    "  - !LinearWarmup\n",
    "    start_factor: 0.\n",
    "    steps: 4000\n",
    "    \n",
    "# 优化器\n",
    "OptimizerBuilder:\n",
    "  optimizer:\n",
    "    momentum: 0.9\n",
    "    type: Momentum\n",
    "    \n",
    "   # 正则化\n",
    "  regularizer:\n",
    "    factor: 0.0005\n",
    "    type: L2\n",
    "```\n"
   ]

   "source": [
    "**数据读取配置文件 yolov3_reader.yml**\n",
    "```\n",
    "worker_num: 1 # 每张GPU reader进程个数\n",
    "TrainReader:\n",
    "# 训练数据transforms\n",
    "  sample_transforms:\n",
    "  - Decode: {}\n",
    "  - RandomResize: {target_size: [[384,1000], [416,1000], [448,1000], [480,1000], [512,1000], [544,1000], [576,1000], [608,1000], [640,1000], [672,1000]], interp: 2, keep_ratio: True}\n",
    "  - RandomFlip: {prob: 0.5}\n",
    "  - AutoAugment: {autoaug_type: v1}\n",
    "   #归一化数值由作业二得到。\n",
    "  - NormalizeImage: {is_scale: true, mean: [0.1548795 , 0.18258693, 0.21738445], std: [0.229, 0.224,0.225]}\n",
    "  - Permute: {}\n",
    "  batch_transforms:\n",
    "  - PadBatch: {pad_to_stride: 32}\n",
    "   # 训练时batch_size \n",
    "  batch_size: 2\n",
    "  # 读取数据是是否乱序\n",
    "  shuffle: true\n",
    "  # 是否丢弃最后不能完整组成batch的数据\n",
    "  drop_last: true\n",
    "  collate_batch: false\n",
    "  use_shared_memory: true\n",
    "\n",
    "#同训练数据\n",
    "EvalReader:\n",
    "  sample_transforms:\n",
    "  - Decode: {}\n",
